    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a Variable M Differential Lock, it offers unparalleled mechanical feedback. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the structural integrity of the high-revving internals. The chassis remains taut with EDC (Electronic Damping Control) functioning perfectly, while the carbon fiber roof lowers the center of gravity for optimized cornering kinematics. A driver-focused specimen with a clean subframe and consistent compression across all eight cylinders.",
