      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster, showing only minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seats remain firm and supple, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracking. All interior features, including the high-fidelity sound system, navigation, and heated seats, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and a recent oil change. The transmission shifts smoothly, and the engine runs quiet and strong. It comes with a complete set of floor mats, two keys, and a detailed folder of service records demonstrating a history of proactive maintenance. This is a solid, honest car ready for many more miles of enjoyment.",
